flowchart TD
    Start["upgrade_single(cli)"] --> FindSpec["查找 CliSpec"]
    FindSpec --> FindBin["find_all_paths(binary)<br/>获取第一个路径"]
    FindBin --> Resolve["resolve_symlink → detect_package_manager"]

    Resolve --> PM{安装方式?}

    PM -->|homebrew-cask| Brew["brew upgrade --cask claude-code"]
    PM -->|homebrew| BrewPkg["brew upgrade &lt;pkg&gt;"]
    PM -->|nvm / fnm / volta / npm| Npm["sibling npm install -g &lt;pkg&gt;@latest<br/>+ NPM_CONFIG_PREFIX"]
    PM -->|system / unknown| Builtin{有 builtin_update?}

    Builtin -->|Yes| BuiltinCmd["claude update / codex update"]
    Builtin -->|No| FallbackNpm["npm install -g &lt;pkg&gt;@latest"]

    Brew --> Run
    BrewPkg --> Run
    Npm --> Run
    BuiltinCmd --> Run
    FallbackNpm --> Run

    Run["run_in_login_shell(cmd)"] --> RunResult{执行结果?}

    RunResult -->|Err| Fail["❌ success: false<br/>error: stderr"]
    RunResult -->|Ok output| ParseOutput["extract_fallback_cmd(output)"]

    ParseOutput --> HasFallback{输出中有<br/>brew/npm 命令?}
    HasFallback -->|Yes| RunFallback["run_in_login_shell(fallback)"]
    HasFallback -->|No| Compare

    RunFallback --> FBResult{fallback 结果?}
    FBResult -->|Err| Fail
    FBResult -->|Ok| Compare

    Compare["对比版本:<br/>prev vs new"] --> Changed{版本变了?}
    Changed -->|Yes| OK["✅ success: true<br/>newVersion"]
    Changed -->|No| Unchanged["❌ success: false<br/>version_unchanged"]
